snippet.title: PM Modi Address after Laying Foundation Stone for Mopa Greenfield Airport in Goa

localized.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi lays foundation stone for Mopa greenfield airport in Goa. In Goa during his speech PM Modi got emotional and requested the peoples of India to give him only 50 days till 30th December to curb black money, corruption, terrorism and fake money in the country. Marriages are affecting after the ban on Rs 500 and 1000 currency notes as families don't have cash in hand to spend.
